node.text: FRUITY FAM! After the celeb bball meet and greet event, I decided to walk around the night market and scope out the place for some good eats,, and I ended up running into a lot of you guys!!! ♥️ I had such a great time meeting y’all and taking pics with y’all! 😄 I love you guys so much you’re all so so amazing, adorable and SWEET 😭♥️ We couldn’t film the ENTIRE time so not everyone I met is in this short clip , i’m sorry! 😚 i’m sure we will meet again! 💕 i’m so happy! thank you from the very bottom of my 心心 ❤️ 我愛您們 😘

-
thank you A1 Canada Sole distributor -Chevalier Star Trading 💖
